              services
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400">
            7. Limitation of Liability
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
            In no event shall AI Apps Directory, nor its directors, employees,
